name: Der Pilz
description:
Mushroom. Ambiguous ambiexterity. Half half. A lift at the end of the tunnel. All those stairs sometimes you know? There's a flower in the eye and two in the bush, and, she sure does have a lot of bush, eh?

-

Fountain pen and coloured pencil on paper, digitized and, reverbalized. 10 edition OBJKT.
